      <title>瑞典 LKAB 与 EQT 支持的初创公司签署绿色水泥协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/sweden-s-lkab-signs-green-cement-deal-with-eqt-backed-startup</link>
